Data.CultureInvariantString: The Less-Lethal Mk 18 Mod 0 is a modified Mk 18, designed to fire Simunition rounds for training and non-lethal engagements. Featuring a 10.3-inch barrel, it maintains the original’s manoeuvrability and reliability. Ideal for tactical training and crowd control, it reduces the risk of injury during operations.
